So if you decide to download Process Lasso from our site, then you should not have such problems, since the program will redistribute priorities between the running applications, which is what makes it possible to achieve 100 percent load reduction from the processes of the downloaded systems, and to reduce the load to a minimum. 
Process Lasso allows us to fully control the running processes, as well as to distribute the resources of the programs, now it's enough just to mark the priority processes and what programs will be responsible for them, there will be nothing superfluous, no more you are not afraid of any loads.
